{"tid":691948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵駛往柴灣遇大雨滲水　網民形容車門變「瀑布」","createTime":"2018-06-06T07:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T15:36:27.000Z","uid":41818,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"08aa89e04eb6aeb1d1c1b0232f7194f7308923e0","tid":691948,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180606/s00001/4409bb6af2075a9d5d2ba8c337731ca4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180606%2Fs00001%2F4409bb6af2075a9d5d2ba8c337731ca4.jpg&h=10a3ddcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港受熱帶低氣壓影響，出現狂風暴雨天氣。有網民在Facebook專頁「西環變幻時」上載影片，稱港鐵列車車門在下大雨時滲水，雨水流入車廂，「一落雨就入水，搞錯咗呀港鐵？」網民以「瀑布」形容該場景。<br />\n<br />\n該名網民回覆《明報》查詢時表示，事發於昨晚8時16分，他搭乘港島線列車在駛離杏花邨站、前往柴灣站，其間見外面下起大雨，約1分鐘後，列車因需等待前一班列車從月台離開，而短暫停留。網民指不久後他面前第二卡的車門開始入水，於是舉機拍攝車內情況。他說，在停止錄影後再發現背後另一道門亦同樣滲水，故隨即離開該處。他直言：「好彩無電死，車頂有高壓電」。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》正就事件向港鐵查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180606/s00001/1528260722864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180606%2Fs00001%2F1528260722864&d=TTCSStd0SLCqKvy40WHKmtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=6a30870a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180606%2Fs00001%2F1528260722864&h=d5241b91\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180606/s00001/1528260722864</a>"},{"pid":"5676b1a8ea7ba67c29e50718f42c01688ac2b161","tid":691948,"uid":110575,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"再嘈我再加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83097c07661cb85aeb7fa00be7143c5d6e114b35","tid":691948,"uid":95,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T09:39:31.000Z","msg":"試過搭東通線道門都滲水。仲要當時架車逼滿人，我就逼左係道門度。<img src=\"/